<br>
Stun<br>
Stun<br>
Slow<br>
Mes<br>
Root<br>
Rune or Theft of Thought<br>
<br>
If a Shaman is grouped with me I take out the slow and replace it with either charm or another stun depending on where I am. ALWAYS ALWAYS protect the Cleric, or healer. That is my first primary goal. If anything is on my healer I am not happy, even if 3 things are on the tank. Stun mez, stun mez, stun mez. I dont like AE mez, it costs too much mana and doesnt last very long. <br>
